item.title: CVE-2023-32478|2024-10-21T13:06:57.292Z -- dell -- powerstore
item.description: Dell PowerStore versions prior to 3.5.0.1 contain an insertion of sensitive information into log file vulnerability. A high privileged malicious user could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to sensitive information disclosure.
